p: Ah Young being first duly sworn on his oath says that he is the petitioner above named that he has heard read the foregoing petition knows the contents and that the same is true
Signed in my presence and sworn to before me this 14 day of Sept 1889.
Let a writ of Habeas Corpus issue as prayed returnable at five o'clock P.M/ this day, Sept 14. 1889.
